This program should be run on MacOS with make -f Makefile.mac run
Two windows open, "Window 2" in front of the main window named "Assignment 3".
In Window 2, change color of the objects by typing a key, 'r' - red, 'g' - green, 'b' - blue, 'y' - yellow, 'o' - orange, 'p' - purple, 'w' - white
In Main Window, change color and start/stop animation via right-click on anywhere in main window (excepting subwindow in top left)
In Main Window, subwindow in top-left corner, change background color via right-click on subwindow
Press 'q' to exit the execution of make run 
